data.text:
Michelle Williams and Heath Ledger dated from June, 2004 to September, 2007.

They had a daughter named Matilda Rose age 18.

On Screen Matchups

Michelle Williams and Heath Ledger were in Brokeback Mountain(2005) together.

About

Michelle Williams is a 43 year old American Actress. Born Michelle Ingrid Williams on 9th September, 1980 in Kalispell, Montana, USA, she is famous for Dawson's Creek, Brokeback Mountain, Blue Valentine, My Week With Marilyn, The Greatest Showman. Her zodiac sign is Virgo.

Australian Actor Heath Ledger was born Heath Andrew Ledger on 4th April, 1979 in Perth, Western Australia, Australia and passed away on 22nd Jan 2008 Soho, Manhattan, New York City, New York, USA aged 28. He is most remembered for his roles as Toby Ackland in the 1997 teen drama thriller film Blackrock, Patrick Verona in the 1999 teen romantic comedy film 10 Things I Hate About You, Gabriel Martin in the 2000 epic historical war drama film The Patriot, William Thatcher in the 2001 medieval action comedy film A Knight's Tale, Sonny Grotowski in the 2001 romantic drama film Monsterâ€™s Ball, Alex Bernier in the 2003 mystery thriller film The Order, Ned Kelly in the 2003 bushranger film Ned Kelly, Skip Engblom in the 2005 biographical drama film Lords of Dogtown, Jacob Grimm in the 2005 fantasy adventure film The Brothers Grimm, Ennis Del Mar in the 2005 neo-Western romantic drama film Brokeback Mountain, Giacomo Casanova in the 2005 romantic comedy-drama film Casanova, Dan in the 2006 romantic drama film Candy, the Joker in the 2008 superhero thriller film The Dark Knight, and Tony Shepard in the 2009 fantasy film The Imaginarium of Doctor Parnassus. His zodiac sign is Aries.
